<author>for KING &amp; COUNTRY</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1) Zo, sun ce mi-ni, pa rum pum pum pum.
 An hai-fi sar-kin-mu, pa rum pum pum pum.
 Mun ka-wo kyau-tai can, pa rum pum pum pum.
 Za mu je wu-rin shi, pa rum pum pum pum,
 rum pum pum pum, rum pum pum pum,
 Za mu ya-be shi, pa rum pum pum pum,
 Inda mun zo.

[V2]
 2) Ja-ri-ri Yesu, pa rum pum pum pum.
 I-na da ta-lau-ci,  pa rum pum pum pum.
 Ban da kyau-ta ba, pa rum pum pum pum .
 Sai wan-nan gan-ga-na, pa rum pum pum, pum, rum pum pum pum, rum pum pum pum,
 Na i-ya bu-ga shi, pa rum pum pum pum,
 In kun so?

[V3]
 3) Ma-ry ta gyaɗa, pa rum pum pum pum.
 Is-sou, ya yin yarda, pa rum pum pum pum.
 Na buga masu shi, pa rum pum pum pum.
 Na bu-ga gan-ga-na, pa rum pum pum pum,
 rum pum pum pum, rum pum pum pum,
 Yesu, yayin mur-mu-shi, pa rum pum pum pum.
 Do-min-a</lyrics>
<title>Yaro Mai Ganga LW561</title>
</song>